{"tid":1649411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"忠告: 唔好喺Twitter直接屌柒Donald Trump. 唔好再裝修Starbucks","createTime":"2019-10-12T15:50:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T02:18:59.000Z","uid":134071,"like":37,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"f04bc26497bb6544739b77739c0c62e22591f536","tid":1649411,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T15:50:37.000Z","msg":"1) 見到有人係Twitter直接tag Donald Trump, 之後屌柒Donald Trump放棄香港.... <strong>呢個係非常傻既行為, 千萬唔好咁做. </strong><br />\n<br />\nDonald Trump受軟唔受硬, 你係Twitter直接tag佢屌柒佢, 佢可能只會更加唔撚理香港示威, 亦可能令共和黨人對香港示威者有壞印象.<br />\n<br />\n大家可以繼續係twitter求Donald Trump幫香港, 繼續求兩黨政客幫香港.  但大家記住: 對美國兩黨政客都要<strong>be humble</strong>. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2) 美國共和黨的長期黨員Mark Simon早已建議不要「裝修」像Starbucks這類跟外資有關的商店.<br />\n<a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1643847/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lihkg.com/thread/1643847/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n但今日, 好似又有Starbucks被裝修? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實真係不建議再裝修跟Starbucks這類跟外資有關的商店....  而且, 美心咁多機構, 好多都跟外資無關....<br />\n<br />\n最後, 講一句<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港, 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"da030099a22f99d094eb3a4594589eb04965b6b7","tid":1649411,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T15:51:34.000Z","msg":"只係我既小小建議, 非大台<br />\n<br />\n大家加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f8dda985217a65823608093d3f2eb1785deff7a","tid":1649411,"uid":130950,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T15:51:55.000Z","msg":"第一項<br />\n屌呀 邊撚個咁撚on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c0e44cb761b9005b4607cd3d5f9d8f4bc8c8057","tid":1649411,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T15:52